{"tid":1801852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有一件好想和理非克服，唔容易但好重要","createTime":"2019-12-29T03:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T03:55:27.000Z","uid":16086,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"84fe5d4c62931923ac23586005c5747a86c1b980","tid":1801852,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:44:21.000Z","msg":"只要你身上係冇Gear，請你唔好驚班狗，<br />\n光明正大咁面對啲狗就得，<br />\n唔好一見到狗就掉轉頭跑。<br />\n<br />\n我明依家班狗係癲嘅，無論你有冇做過咩都有機會拉你，唔好彩仲會打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係係時候要克服啦，依家班狗成班黑社會咁，但係你地記唔記得佢地係市民嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">公僕</span></span>呀！<br />\n<br />\n我唔要再見到有人跪，<br />\n亦唔想大家一見到班狗就驚到掉頭走。<br />\n<br />\n和理非，依個進化唔易，<br />\n因為依家班狗真係好撚癲，<br />\n但係希望講出黎之後，<br />\n大家可以慢慢克服！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdacd682a73123a584c2cf12adbc0a29f28321c5","tid":1801852,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:45:36.000Z","msg":"僕你老母<br />\n重當班狗係香港人<br />\n弱智"},{"pid":"51d113f2d59906949479f719c75ace9cf0f429fa","tid":1801852,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:47:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f24cd42e8fbe29e238c0d095d40e62f61a603d0d","tid":1801852,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:47:40.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"097065c3238e918a16c0bb300edb5dfe29cfd5c7","tid":1801852,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdacd682a73123a584c2cf12adbc0a29f28321c5","tid":1801852,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:45:36.000Z","msg":"僕你老母<br />\n重當班狗係香港人<br />\n弱智"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:47:44.000Z","msg":"唔好意思手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你有道理<br />\n不過重點都係想大家唔好咁易驚班狗"},{"pid":"30fee5b2140062829ee699e802b84eb725dda11b","tid":1801852,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51d113f2d59906949479f719c75ace9cf0f429fa","tid":1801852,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:47:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:52:05.000Z","msg":"月娥你冷靜啲先，唔係話唔走，<br />\n但係唔係一見到班狗就走，<br />\n班狗真係兇9你先好退，<br />\n唔好街頭見到狗，街尾就走定先。"},{"pid":"6096f64690cec25b8318c7372a43db6e26d143a3","tid":1801852,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:53:53.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1c3345519dd5dac475383814864f40c5600d4aea","tid":1801852,"uid":16086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:54:30.000Z","msg":"香港警察死全家"},{"pid":"707e25cb1226cb453482a4b6a0f666502107c399","tid":1801852,"uid":2584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T03:55:27.000Z","msg":"甴近平"}]}